{"tid":467982,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現同事對我個女有興趣，點算？","createTime":"2017-11-14T03:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T18:56:52.000Z","uid":143768,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e191c4266b3d1415c77ef089a97af3f17f598b1","tid":467982,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"班同事不嬲都冇乜問題，係把口衰少少，但都係普通打工仔啦<br />\n有一次返工漏咗個file係屋企，入面夾咗張支票，趕住即日入，<br />\n咪睇下屋企有冇人可以拎嚟公司<br />\n嗰日咁啱個女唔使返學，就叫佢拎嚟啦<br />\n點知就好似出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀女一嚟到公司，條mk同事就即刻起痰咁問佢有咩事，有咩幫到佢<br />\n到佢知道佢係我個女之後，好似仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得仲大機會可以識佢<br />\n<br />\n而家佢成日問關於我個女啲野，又成日搵藉口想上我屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點撚算"},{"pid":"ac35b5f93fc34ef961dd054d9e6ed7cc47704632","tid":467982,"uid":76697,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T03:59:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58fb90b331d28d47033a4f40ab2d4ee2ae0fc352","tid":467982,"uid":143768,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"仆街 同事負皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪搞我個女"},{"pid":"500ff1e7eb8b5c659e823ccbcb232ca809ef532b","tid":467982,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介紹比我<br />\n<br />\n我溝左你個女<br />\n<br />\n你同事就冇望</blockquote><br />\n唔想俾個女識啲唔男唔女既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a132640871e67ac6918688d2f8378a4dd4d651f6","tid":467982,"uid":153471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"郁佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df1ed994b718e963951993bb2ec95489861c8b5","tid":467982,"uid":